{
  "stem": "21089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the birth certificate, I-- very seldom was a birth certificate where somebody-- but I know my-- know why I don't-- didn't have-- my father was a religious man.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he-- and his name on document was Jacob, which is-- it was Jekov, which is Polish name, Helenah, which is also Polish name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it was father's and mother's name in the birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I just used those documents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also had some Lithuanian document because I was working on a housing project.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is from Ger-- from Lithuanian authorities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't also that I am Jew or not Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So those are the only documents which I had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I went not through the main highway, but through the field that I knew going east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I asked where it to go to the-- and finally, I came to the village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I asked-- I said that I am-- as I heard from such and such men-- he wasn't a Jew-- that he's looking.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this man was the only Gentile who knew that I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody-- is that-- that time, men, Gentiles knew that I'm a Jew, but he knew that I am going-- he gave me the address.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he knew that I'm-- nobody knew where I went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to, to the fellow, and I asked for a job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, all my life, I was a farmer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He look at my hands, and I saw a smirk on his face.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, are you looking at my hands?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are not farmer's hands, but I said I was studying in Vienna, so I-- but my father had the farm.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
